"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"This year has been uneasy for Chinese Crypto Community. First, the government banned crypto mining, then shut down crypto exchanges, OTC, and then Fiat onramp and offramp. And finally, it forced all the crypto news/medium platform to close their service. As a result, one of my favorite Chinese Crypto News platform, Chainnews.com, has closed its service. I used to read their crypto news almost everyday, but now, when I click the link, it shows ‚ÄúThis site can‚Äôt be reached‚Äù. I feel so sad that it was shut down because of the censorship. \\n\\nThis makes me think what can be done to avoid censorship like this onward. I think web3 will be the future. First, we have decentralized storage (such as Arweave), so we no longer rely on those centralized data center to save the contents, then those medium can publish their news on decentralized blockchain. No government can shut it down. \\n\\nIf year 2021 marks the beginning of web3, we will see the exponential growth in next ten years. It was the best of times, it was NOT the worst of times. \\n\\nWAGMI. üöÄüöÄüöÄ\",\"timestamp\":1638155497,\"title\":\"Some thoughts on decentralized medium\"},\"digest\":\"qgOWAz5CrdQW4GPFMoh8FT2VEBkFzYzw_yaW-_6GGqM\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x6ea5eB80b326835df1804B9c2a574E6082aa2d22\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"gFghG0JhKbsLWNJorjxKAVkP0QFu1_6PziJa7KTgMCw\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"vUmk1q9EHE2s7EMKfXCbVaqPhDVhsntr9zfatxr4jmw\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"b39_FgmYF9bSVXJE-D25YbKJI_F9j41nkv722VvdFE3vMT3DWQTvl84wL0Yax3ACcFGq0xdLF0vVtDsRV_Cg0A\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x114fcc880ea4d23ca24152e91693bfc4502de48d09188c6ff405f8b4f1bb2bf56f074d7596b47e5d92aadf05d56db78a9b44923e56d5ebae64e2dae099b6f95c1c\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\